title: Houmous and olive sandwich spread
ingredients: ['35g pitted Kalamata olives, drained', '20g pitted green olives', '225g prepared houmous', '1 tablespoon tahini', '1 teaspoon finely chopped fresh flat leaf parsley', '1 teaspoon finely chopped fresh rosemary', '1/2 teaspoon ground coriander', '1/8 teaspoon garlic powder', '1/8 teaspoon onion powder', '1/8 teaspoon ground black pepper']
